{"tid":2072783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸開始清理香港公務員","createTime":"2020-06-21T00:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T00:36:10.000Z","uid":17831,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f56594d7dc2a5203247bcbdaf406d05a8e1efcc6","tid":2072783,"uid":17831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"向警察致警呢個Page 開始配合未成立既置安法去助攻清理香港公務員<br />\n<br />\n想提下<br />\n1. 香港既公務員係時候要刪Facebook page/文章。<br />\n因為佢地會攪到你鐵飯碗都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 未落國安法都咁惡，請小心不斷上網上線，因為係大陸紅官上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 而家只係Facebook 講野都危險，有「國家部隊」， 可能將來檢查手機whatsapp，室內收音，一聽到反共言論就捉返去國安部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 溫水煮蛙，而家會先攪制服團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 幫手Push 下比黃既公務員....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xc28DdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxc28DdW.png&h=e1aa284a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b7d4c99d2f728300f6f688dc272e4652c97f21f","tid":2072783,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:03:36.000Z","msg":"仲大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff27636e6106af287a9574ead873a9c9de75c7ba","tid":2072783,"uid":17831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>向警察致警呢個Page 開始配合未成立既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國安法</span></strong>去助攻清理香港公務員<br />\n<br />\n想提下<br />\n1. 香港既公務員係時候要刪Facebook page/文章。<br />\n因為佢地會攪到你鐵飯碗都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 未<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成立</span></strong>國安法都咁惡，請小心不斷<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">上綱上線</span></strong>，因為係大陸紅官上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class